utauqua Talk.\nMiss Mtrlatn J. Goldberg, of the\nJewish Chautauqua Society,, will\n<>peak at. the Eighth Street Temple\non Thursday night. She will tell\nof the purposes and program of\nthe annual convention of the Chau\ntauqua Society which will be held\nin Washington the last week In\nDecember.\nSKILLED BRITISH LABOR\nIS RUSHINC TO AMERICA\nLONDON, Oct. 12.\u2014Laments that\nGreat Britain is being drained of\nher best craftsmen because of un\nemployment here and the superior\nattractions of the United States\nlabor market are becoming frequent\nin the press. This loss is said to be\ncausing concern to \"employers and\nlabor leaders because the skill of\nthese workers is necessary to the\nwelfare pf British industry, and be\ncause tnelr departure rapidly In\ncreases the number of unskilled\nmen among the unemployed.\nSteel plant employes and the\nshipbuilders are the chief, although\nnot the only, emigrants. Their\ngoal is Invariably the United States,\nwhere they are said to be snapped\nup eagerly.\nThe Daily Mall quotes Chairman\nBrownlie, of the Amalgamated Engi\nneers Union, as saying that Amer\nica is -reaping the benefit of the\nBritish apprenticeship system,\nwhich does not exist in the United\nStates. v\nMiner\u2019s Home Dynamited.\nHAZLETON. Pa., Oct. 15. The\nhome of Dominic Carsla was dyna\nmited and the property was damaged\nto a considerable extent, the rear\nporch being torn off. Carsla cannot\naccount for the outrage, and the\npolice have no clew.\nEIGHT-HOUR BASIS FOR\nTIRE COMPANY WORKERS\nCUMBERLAND, Md., Oct. It.\u2014\nAn eight-hour baste for worked of\nthe Kelly-Springfield Tire Company\nwill be established, it is announced\nhy Thomas C. Marshall, vice presi\ndent. Several departments will be\naffected by the policy beginning\ntoday and the 'new schedule Os\nhours will be gradually extended.\nAlso Mr. Marshall said that 1.300\nemployes who. were 4aid off several\nmonths ago had been asked to re\nturn to work and that many men\nwould be employed. He declared\nthe business outlook to be \"most\npromising.\u2019* t","height":"26994","width":"22470"}}
